      <note id="note_cdq_gjz_5gc" type="note" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Failure to follow the recommendation will cause shortened life due to excessive gear
                wear.</p>
      </note>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Select oil that meets below specifications.</p>
      <ul id="ul_h51_r3z_5gc" class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">API GL-5</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">MIL-L-2105 C, D</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Gear Oil offers maximum protection against the scoring and pitting of gear teeth and
            rolling element bearings.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Gear Oil can also provide excellent stability under high temperature conditions and has
            superior low temperature performance. It will also give protection against rust and
            corrosion.</p>
